\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\"><span>עריכה</span></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/index.php?title=%D7%99%D7%A9%D7%A8%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%91%D7%A8%D7%95%D7%9A_%D7%A9%D7%9E%D7%97%D7%94_%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%91%D7%A8%D7%9E%D7%9F&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"עריכת קוד המקור של הפרק: הערות שוליים\"><span>עריכת קוד מקור</span></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">שם פועל היום הרב שלום דובער ויספיש</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<div class=\"stub\" style=\"background-color:#FFFCFC; border-color:#CCCCCC; border-style:double; border-width:3px; clear:both; padding-top:4px; padding-bottom:4px; padding-right:7px; margin:0.5em 0 0.5em 0;vertical-align:middle;\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/index.php/%D7%A7%D7%95%D7%91%D7%A5:%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C_%D7%97%D7%91%D7%93%D7%A4%D7%93%D7%99%D7%94.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/e/e6/%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C_%D7%97%D7%91%D7%93%D7%A4%D7%93%D7%99%D7%94.png/50px-%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C_%D7%97%D7%91%D7%93%D7%A4%D7%93%D7%99%D7%94.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e6/%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C_%D7%97%D7%91%D7%93%D7%A4%D7%93%D7%99%D7%94.png/75px-%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C_%D7%97%D7%91%D7%93%D7%A4%D7%93%D7%99%D7%94.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e6/%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C_%D7%97%D7%91%D7%93%D7%A4%D7%93%D7%99%D7%94.png/100px-%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C_%D7%97%D7%91%D7%93%D7%A4%D7%93%D7%99%D7%94.png 2x\" /></a></span> &#160; ערך זה הוא <a href=\"/index.php/%D7%97%D7%91%22%D7%93%D7%A4%D7%93%D7%99%D7%94:%D7%A7%D7%A6%D7%A8%D7%9E%D7%A8\" title=\"חב&quot;דפדיה:קצרמר\">קצרמר</a>&#160;בנושא <a href=\"/index.php/%D7%A7%D7%98%D7%92%D7%95%D7%A8%D7%99%D7%94:%D7%A7%D7%A6%D7%A8%D7%9E%D7%A8_%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A9%D7%99%D7%9D\" title=\"קטגוריה:קצרמר אישים\">אישים</a>. אתם מו